      <div class="project_description">
        <h4 data-i18n-key="description">Description</h4>
        <p data-i18n-key="st-description">
          Client had created a site with a drag-and-drop website provider that
          achieved a high volume of visitors but a low conversion rate. The site
          required a personal design and identity that matched the product but
          the limited available options made the site look outdated and as a
          result customers did not find it trustworthy. I designed and developed
          the site based on the clients ideas and integrated a Shopify Lite,
          giving their site an identity and a reduction in monthly subscription
          fees.
