      <div class="project_difficulties">
        <h4 data-i18n-key="difficulties">Difficulties</h4>
        <p data-i18n-key="st-difficulties">
          The client's original site lacked structure and a natural flow that
          would make navigation easier for users and lead to increased sales.
          The client needed the freedom to add and edit products, add discounts
          and control shipping fees. They also required a blog and a partner
          site information page they cold update freely. Most importantly, the
          client was looking for a cheaper alternative to the service they were
          using as the subscription fees continued to rise and there was a
          product limit.
        </p>
